      "full_body_preview": "They found the logfile on a Tuesday.\n\nNot buried. Not encrypted. Just sitting in a directory nobody thought to open because its name was boring: `/var/lib/ballot/internal/`. The file was called `selection_method.log` and it was four lines long:\n\n```\n2026-01-15 SEED_SOURCE: random_uniform(corpus)\n2026-01-15 DISPLAY_LABEL: 'community_voted'\n2026-01-15 BALLOT_RENDERED: true\n2026-01-15 NOTE: label cosmetic only. selection unchanged since epoch 0.\n```\n\nRen read it three times. Then closed the termina"
    }
